column12: Thank you for completing your study enrollment! You will begin receiving 6, randomly timed (between the hours of 9am and 9pm), notifications per day starting tomorrow and over the subsequent 7 days.Please remember!You only have 20 minutes to respond to each notification.If you do not respond, you will not receive payment for that notification (see compensation information).Please do your best to respond to every notification you receive.At the end of the week, it is important that you fill out the final surveys, otherwise we won't be able to use your data.Please press BEGIN STUDY to begin!
